author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-WISeKey Prelim FY Pro-Forma Revenue Of $43.5 Million, Up 299 Pct
text:
Feb 23 (Reuters) - WISEKEY INTERNATIONAL HOLDING AG :
* WISEKEY REPORTS STRONG Q4 & FY 2017 PRELIMINARY FINANCIAL RESULTS AND ANNOUNCES INITIAL FY 2018 REVENUE GUIDANCE
* Q4 2017 REVENUES INCREASED BY 49% TO $11.4 MILLION, AS COMPARED TO $7.7 MILLION IN Q4 2016
* 2017 PRELIMINARY UNAUDITED PRO-FORMA REVENUE OF $43.5 MILLION, UP 299% AS COMPARED TO FY 2016
* EXPECTS REVENUE OF APPROXIMATELY $14 MILLION FOR Q1 2018 * FY 2018 REVENUE GUIDANCE OF APPROX $60 MILLION, INCREASE OF APPROX 38% AS COMPARED TO 2017 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
